data.description: Downtown living at its finest.  This unit has been lovingly updated throughout this owner's tenure.  From new wood floors to custom window treatments, she has touched every surface in this home & it shows.  Improvements inc. kitchen cabinets, solid surface countertop extension,  wood slat back splash, light fixtures & ceiling fan, custom industrial railing for loft landing, enclosure of 2nd BR for privacy. Both bathrooms have been updated w/walk-in showers & more. A wall of sliders opens up to a private patio w/views of Mass Ave. Enjoy everything downtown within steps of your new front door. Building has pool, sauna, hot tub & work out room. Dedicated spot in the garage. Please note that Real Silk Lofts is a non-smoking building.
